{\b AI-Usage}\par
\par
A per-user system-tray app that shows your combined Claude and Codex usage at a glance.\par
\par
This installer places the app under your own user profile ({\i %LOCALAPPDATA%\\Programs\\AIUsage}), adds a Start Menu shortcut, and (by default) starts it when you log on. It installs for the current user only and needs no administrator rights. Nothing is written outside your profile.\par
\par
{\b Terms.} This software is provided "as is", without warranty of any kind, express or implied. You install and run it at your own risk. It reads your local Claude and Codex usage data on this machine only.\par
\par
Click {\b Install} to continue.\par
